# filename: int_deduped_returns.sql
```sql
-- Deduplicate returns to select one approved return per item
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        return_id,
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY 
                CASE WHEN status = 'approved' THEN 1 ELSE 2 END,
                return_date ASC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    return_id,
    item_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

# filename: fct_product_performance.sql
```sql
-- Final fact table with product return rates by category
WITH item_sales AS (
    SELECT
        oi.product_id,
        COALESCE(p.category_id, 0) AS category_id
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
        ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
),
sales_by_category AS (
    SELECT
        i.category_id,
        SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_items_sold
    FROM item_sales i
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
        ON oi.product_id = i.product_id
    GROUP BY i.category_id
),
item_returns AS (
    SELECT
        ri.item_id,
        ri.return_date,
        COALESCE(p.category_id, 0) AS category_id
    FROM {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} ri
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
        ON oi.item_id = ri.item_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
        ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
),
returns_by_category AS (
    SELECT
        ir.category_id,
        COUNT(DISTINCT ir.item_id) AS total_items_returned
    FROM item_returns ir
    GROUP BY ir.category_id
),
category_dim AS (
    SELECT
        category_id,
        COALESCE(name, '(unknown)') AS category_name
    FROM {{ ref('stg_categories') }}
)
SELECT
    c.category_name,
    COALESCE(s.total_items_sold, 0) AS total_items_sold,
    COALESCE(r.total_items_returned, 0) AS total_items_returned,
    CASE
        WHEN COALESCE(s.total_items_sold, 0) = 0 THEN 0
        ELSE ROUND(
            COALESCE(r.total_items_returned, 0)::NUMERIC / COALESCE(s.total_items_sold, 0),
            4
        )
    END AS return_rate
FROM category_dim c
LEFT JOIN sales_by_category s
    ON s.category_id = c.category_id
LEFT JOIN returns_by_category r
    ON r.category_id = c.category_id
ORDER BY total_items_returned DESC NULLS LAST
